<item>
            <title>[HIVE-13294] AvroSerde leaks the connection in a case when reading schema from a url</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-13294</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;AvroSerde leaks the connection in a case when reading schema from url:&lt;br/&gt;
In &lt;br/&gt;
public static Schema determineSchemaOrThrowException {&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;br/&gt;
    return AvroSerdeUtils.getSchemaFor(new URL(schemaString).openStream());&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;br/&gt;
The opened inputStream is never closed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
